name: I Heart Japan Sticker - White or Black
description:
I Heart Japan Logo (Designed by Exit Fifteen Apparel)

Die-Cut Sticker: 
Black Text/Red Heart
White Text/Red Heart
Approx: 9"x2"

All Products should be shipped within 1-3 weeks of purchase due to the fact that we have to make the product, package it, and take it to UPS. 

Once more orders are placed shipping will be faster because we will start keeping product in stock.

All profits are being donated to the American Red Cross Japan Relief Fund. Please help out our friends who have been hit by this disaster!
